title: The_Witcher_Books_[all 1-8]_Andrzej_Sapkowski[pdf+kindle+epub]
description:
Includes all the eight witcher series books by Andrzej Sapkowski, numbered in reading order:

01-Short Stories-The_Last_Wish (1993)
02-Short Stories-The_Sword_of_Destiny (1992)
03_Blood_of_Elves (1994)
04_Times_of_Contempt (1995)
05_Baptism_of_Fire (1996)
06_The_Tower_of_the_Swallow (1997)
07_The_Lady_of_the_Lake (1999)
08_Season_of_Storms (2013)

I have personally read all the books and the translation is great, you will enjoy reading them.

Kindle azw3 format has some random spaces and typos placed in some books which is a conversion error and can be ignored. The other formats dont have such errors.

Please seed after download!
